{"tid":380933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]Trump on North Korea: 'Talking is not the answer'","createTime":"2017-08-30T13:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T11:04:12.000Z","uid":4783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4894822e5b76f1c60ed385f4559edbd0a461c21b","tid":380933,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"President Donald Trump on Wednesday expressed frustration that diplomatic efforts with North Korea are not yielding results, tweeting that &quot;talking is not the answer!&quot; after the reclusive country launched its latest missile test earlier this week.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The U.S. has been talking to North Korea, and paying them extortion money, for 25 years,&rdquo; he wrote. &ldquo;Talking is not the answer!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nTrump didn&rsquo;t explain how the U.S. has supposedly paid extortion funds to North Korea, but the U.S. has provided international aid assistance to the country in the past.<br />\n<br />\nDespite Trump&rsquo;s strong words on Wednesday, the president&rsquo;s secretary of state, Rex Tillerson, and defense secretary, Jim Mattis, have stressed that diplomacy and economic pressure applied to North Korea is the best way to deescalate the tension and push the North to denuclearize.<br />\n<br />\nThe president's tweet follows a White House statement issued Tuesday in which the president said &ldquo;all options are on the table&rdquo; in dealing with North Korea.<br />\n<br />\nThe rhetoric between the U.S. and North Korea has intensified this week after North Korea fired a ballistic missile over Japan, a move seen as extremely provocative. The U.N. Security Council denounced the missile launch on Tuesday as &ldquo;outrageous.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nFar from backing down, however, North Korean state media issued a warning Wednesday that the missile fired over Japan was &ldquo;the first step of the military operation &hellip; in the Pacific and a meaningful prelude to containing Guam,&rdquo; according to CNN. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.politico.com/story/2017/08/30/trump-north-korea-tweet-japan-missile-242167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fstory%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2Ftrump-north-korea-tweet-japan-missile-242167&d=mGCV8xnCRzg2tB5yerfWIAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=07b28515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.politico.com/story/2017/08/30/trump-north-korea-tweet-japan-missile-242167</a>"},{"pid":"6845009394e128889c3bcc105c2b581eeadef627","tid":380933,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:28:13.000Z","msg":"講乜春 俾人踩到上心口<br />\n面目無光 颜面無存 真係死淨把口<br />\n嘅口水佬"},{"pid":"58f85c1dc7276ae0189aae631b2258b8020276ce","tid":380933,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:30:58.000Z","msg":"咁撚多爹，無料就收聲啦"},{"pid":"b082385e634f292d332bbe63e87e272751d83b08","tid":380933,"uid":78399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:32:18.000Z","msg":"watching is the answer"},{"pid":"5db67058d0263d0a980d6c09a786f59e20860723","tid":380933,"uid":4783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講乜春 俾人踩到上心口<br />\n面目無光 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">颜</span></span></strong>面無存 真係死淨把口<br />\n嘅口水佬</blockquote>"},{"pid":"24f83ac42002313fb4d0d4adf66ffe8a94e5ab35","tid":380933,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:37:27.000Z","msg":"得依到先會覺得一個民主國家咁易發動戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fec11afa3336ba630a70929d1e75914bed9357","tid":380933,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:38:50.000Z","msg":"Trump仔唔打NK正傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c171d2fe9